#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">Tips for Success<br/><br/></span></strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong><span class=\"h2-fs\">ເຄັດລັບສູ່ຄວາມສຳເລັດ<br/><br/></span></strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Accounting</strong>: Automate invoices, reconcile payments, and "
"track profitability per tour type"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການບັນຊີ</strong>: ອອກໃບເກັບເງິນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ, ກວດສອບການຊຳລະເງິນ, ແລະ ຕິດຕາມກ"
"ຳໄລຕາມປະເພດຂອງທົວ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Activate the multilingual website setting to localize your website "
"to international audiences.</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເປີດໃຊ້ການຕັ້ງຄ່າເວັບໄຊແບບຫຼາຍພາສາ ເພື່ອປັບແຕ່ງເວັບໄຊຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຜູ້ຊົມທົ່ວໂລກ.</"
"strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Antwerp</strong> dazzles with its fashion-forward spirit and rich "
"artistic heritage. Explore the legacy of Rubens, marvel at the gothic "
"Cathedral of Our Lady, and stroll through the dynamic streets of this port "
"city where tradition meets modern creativity."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແອນເວີບ (Antwerp)</strong> ໂດດເດັ່ນດ້ວຍຈິດວິນຍານແຫ່ງແຟຊັນ ແລະ ມໍລະດົກທາງສິລະປະທີ່ອຸ"
"ດົມສົມບູນ. ສຳຫຼວດມໍລະດົກຂອງ Rubens, ຊົມຄວາມງາມຂອງໂບດ Cathedral of Our Lady ແບບໂກທິກ, "
"ແລະ ຍ່າງເລາະຕາມຖະໜົນທີ່ທັນສະໄໝຂອງເມືອງທ່າເຮືອແຫ່ງນີ້ ບ່ອນທີ່ປະເພນີມາພົບກັບຄວາມຄິດສ້າງສັນຍຸກໃໝ່."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Appointments</strong>: Allow customers to book private tours based "
"on availability and language preferences."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ການນັດໝາຍ</strong>: ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຈອງທົວສ່ວນຕົວ ໂດຍອີງຕາມເວລາຫວ່າງ ແລະ ພາສາທີ່ຕ້"
"ອງການ."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Apps &amp; What They Do:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ແອັບຕ່າງໆ &amp; ໜ້າທີ່ຂອງພວກມັນ:</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Brussels</strong>, the heart of Europe, welcomes you with grand "
"architecture, cobblestone streets, and a vibrant atmosphere. From the "
"opulent Grand Place to the surreal world of Magritte, this city is a must-"
"see for culture lovers and history buffs alike."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ບຣຸກແຊນ (Brussels)</strong>, ຫົວໃຈຂອງເອີຣົບ, ຍິນດີຕ້ອນຮັບທ່ານດ້ວຍສະຖາປັດຕະຍະກຳທີ່ຍິ່"
"ງໃຫຍ່, ຖະໜົນຫີນທີ່ສວຍງາມ, ແລະ ບັນຍາກາດທີ່ມີຊີວິດຊີວາ. ຕັ້ງແຕ່ Grand Place ທີ່ຫຼູຫຼາ ໄປຈົນເຖິງໂລກສິລະ"
"ປະຂອງ Magritte, ເມືອງນີ້ແມ່ນສະຖານທີ່ທີ່ຜູ້ຮັກວັດທະນະທຳ ແລະ ປະຫວັດສາດບໍ່ຄວນພາດ."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create services</strong> for each destination &amp; language pair"
msgstr "<strong>ສ້າງການບໍລິການ</strong> ສຳລັບແຕ່ລະຈຸດໝາຍປາຍທາງ &amp; ຄູ່ພາສາ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create visually rich pages</strong> with images, videos, and tour "
"descriptions"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງໜ້າເວັບທີ່ສວຍງາມ</strong> ດ້ວຍຮູບພາບ, ວິດີໂອ, ແລະ ຄຳອະທິບາຍທົວ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customers book online</strong> and receive <strong>automated "
"reminders</strong>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ລູກຄ້າຈອງອອນລາຍ</strong> ແລະ ຮັບ <strong>ການແຈ້ງເຕືອນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong>"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Customize layouts easily</strong> using drag-and-drop editor"
msgstr "<strong>ປັບແຕ່ງຮູບແບບໄດ້ງ່າຍໆ</strong> ໂດຍໃຊ້ຕົວແກ້ໄຂແບບລາກ ແລະ ວາງ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Dashboards</strong>: Visualize your KPIs—bookings per guide, top-"
"selling tours, revenue trends"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ແຜງຄວບຄຸມ</strong>: ເບິ່ງຂໍ້ມູນ KPI ຂອງທ່ານ—ການຈອງຕໍ່ຜູ້ນຳທ່ຽວ, ທົວທີ່ຂາຍດີທີ່ສຸດ, ແນວໂນ້"
"ມລາຍໄດ້"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Define each tour</strong> as an event with time slots and capacities"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ກຳນົດແຕ່ລະທົວ</strong> ເປັນກິດຈະກຳທີ່ມີຊ່ວງເວລາ ແລະ ຈຳນວນຄົນທີ່ຮອງຮັບໄດ້"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Define guide availability</strong> per service"
msgstr "<strong>ກຳນົດເວລາຫວ່າງຂອງຜູ້ນຳທ່ຽວ</strong> ຕໍ່ການບໍລິການ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Digital tickets with QR codes</strong> for easy on-site check-in"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕົວດິຈິຕອນທີ່ມີລະຫັດ QR</strong> ເພື່ອຄວາມສະດວກໃນການເຊັກອິນຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Enable online booking &amp; payment</strong>, no manual follow-up "
"needed"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເປີດໃຊ້ການຈອງ &amp; ການຊຳລະເງິນອອນລາຍ</strong>, ບໍ່ຈຳເປັນຕ້ອງຕິດຕາມດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Events</strong>: Set up group tours with schedules and manage "
"bookings and attendance."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ກິດຈະກຳ</strong>: ຕັ້ງຄ່າທົວແບບກຸ່ມດ້ວຍຕາຕະລາງເວລາ ແລະ ຈັດການການຈອງ ແລະ ການເຂົ້າ"
"ຮ່ວມ."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.ir_ui_view_3840
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> enchants with medieval splendor and a youthful "
"energy. Discover castles, canals, and hidden alleyways as you uncover the "
"soul of a city where past and present coexist in perfect harmony."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເກນ (Ghent)</strong> ສ້າງຄວາມປະທັບໃຈດ້ວຍຄວາມຮຸ່ງເຮືອງຍຸກກາງ ແລະ ພະລັງຂອງໄວໜຸ່"
"ມ. ຄົ້ນພົບປາສາດ, ຄອງນ້ຳ, ແລະ ເສັ້ນທາງລັບໆ ໃນຂະນະທີ່ທ່ານສຳຜັດກັບຈິດວິນຍານຂອງເມືອງ ບ່ອນທີ່ອະດີດ ແລ"
"ະ ປັດຈຸບັນຢູ່ຮ່ວມກັນຢ່າງລົງຕົວ."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
msgid ""
"<strong>Ghent</strong> is the kind of city that sneaks up on you — and "
"steals your heart. A vibrant mix of gothic spires, canalside charm, artistic"
" rebellion, and youthful energy, Ghent is one of Belgium’s best-kept "
"secrets… though the word is definitely getting out."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເກນ (Ghent)</strong> ແມ່ນເມືອງທີ່ຈະເຮັດໃຫ້ທ່ານຫຼົງຮັກໂດຍບໍ່ຮູ້ຕົວ. ດ້ວຍການປະສົມປະສານທີ່ລົ"
"ງຕົວຂອງ ຍອດຫໍຄອຍແບບໂກທິກ, ສະເໜ່ແຄມຄອງນ້ຳ, ສິລະປະທີ່ທ້າທາຍ, ແລະ ພະລັງຂອງໄວໜຸ່ມ, ເກນແມ່ນໜຶ່ງໃນ"
"ຄວາມລັບທີ່ສວຍງາມທີ່ສຸດຂອງແບນຊິກ."

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:guided_tours.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Handle walk-in traffic</strong> efficiently with synced stock"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຈັດການລູກຄ້າທີ່ຍ່າງເຂົ້າມາ</strong> ຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບດ້ວຍການເຊື່ອມໂຍງຂໍ້ມູນບ່ອນຫວ່າງ"

#. module: guided_tours
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_1
#: model_terms:event.event,description:guided_tours.event_event_2
